</style>
<p>
<p>Does the semi-variogram suggest that dependence decreases with an increasing distance between spatial sites?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>We can create the semi-variogram using</p>
<pre><code>Meuse &lt;- read.csv(&quot;Meuse.csv&quot;)

coordinates( Meuse ) &lt;- ~Lon+Lat
gamma_hat &lt;- variogram( zinc~1, Meuse )

ggplot( gamma_hat, aes( x=dist, y=gamma/2 ) ) + geom_point( size=2 ) + 
  theme_bw() + labs( x=&quot;Distance&quot;, y=&quot;Semi-variogram&quot; )</code></pre>
<p>We find that the value in the semi-variogram increases with increasing spatial distance. We thus conclude that the dependence decreases with an increasing distance between sites.</p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
